# Edge Function secrets (server-side; NOT shipped to the client).
#
# Copy to `supabase/functions/.env` for local runs (`supabase functions serve`)
# and set the matching secret on the DB webhook's Authorization header. SUPABASE_URL
# and SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY are auto-injected by the Supabase runtime and need
# not be set locally. Spec: docs/specs/spec-mate-push.md.

# Shared secret the shared_state DB webhook must send as `Authorization: Bearer
# <PUSH_WEBHOOK_SECRET>`. The push-dispatcher rejects any request without it.
PUSH_WEBHOOK_SECRET=replace-with-a-long-random-string
